tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush power-play goal and it's 16-9! Ryan Keenan collects his hat trick goal as he's left alone in the slot and he guns it home.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 15-9! Mike Messenger sheds the check of the defender right in front of the crease and then neatly tucks a shot under the arm of Vinc.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal to make it 14-9! Big save by Evan Kirk at one end, then Jeremy Thompson sprints the floor and sets up Matt Hossack for the clutch transition goal.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 13-8! After a 3 on 1 doesn't work, Robert Church wiggles his way past the defender and then fires it in for his fourth of the night.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 12-6! Ryan Keenan gets some room on the wing and then lets an absolute rocket go that finds the top corner. Second of the night.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 11-6! Marty Dinsdale goes around the corner on the wing, grabs the pass from Robert Church and flings a sidearm shot that sneaks by Vinc.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 10-4! Mark Matthews left all alone on the wing, steps up and unleashes a rocket. K-Hawks pull Vinc and Angus Goodleaf goes into the net.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal to make it 9-4! Ryan Keenan goes one on one with the defender, twists, turns and finally goes airborne to send the shot by Vinc.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 8-4! Brett Mydske quick feed up the floor to Jeff Cornwall who sends a wicked shot inside the far post.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 7-4! Jeff Cornwall with the huge defensive play, he then tears up the turf to the other end and sets up Ben McIntosh for the finish.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 6-4! Natural hat trick for Robert Church! He cuts into the slot to grab the errant pass/loose ball, cruises into the slot and zips his shot in.

tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 5-4! Robert Church second goal in a row as he peels around the defender, snares the perfect pass from Marty Dinsdale and then finishes off.

tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush shorthanded goal and it's 4-4! Robert Church battles thru hold, drives past second defender, and then rifles it in.

tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 3-2! Ben McIntosh cuts to the net blows right by his defender, grabs the hot pass from Jeff Shattler and buries it past Vinc.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 2-2! Jeff Cornwall cashes in on the rebound off the endboards, tucking it past Vinc.

tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 1-0! Jeremy Thompson snares the long-bomb feed from Evan Kirk, goes right at the d-man and guns a sub-shot right thru Vinc.

tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 9-4. Ryan Keenan on the power play as he takes the backhand flip pass from Mark Matthews and goes far corner.

tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal to make it 13-7. Robert Church finds seam between two defenders in tight, grabs the pass and puts it away. Terrific play all around by Rush offence.

tweet: HE SCORES! Quick strike on the PP for @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 12-7. Ben McIntosh off edge of the crease takes the pass and one-times it home easy-peasy.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush shorthanded goal by Jeff Cornwall to make it 11-5. Four-goal run for Rush as Cornwall storms up field, steps into slot and unleashes one past Poulin.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal in transition again and it's 10-5. Rookie Nick Finlay, playing in his first NLL game, leads the breakout, dishes to Brett Mydske and he fires it home.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush make it 9-5! Chris Corbeil leads the transition, drop pass to Matt Hossack and he undresses Poulin with a beauty move.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 8-5! Jeff Shattler collects his hat trick marker with a quick-stick release after a great pass across the crease from Ben McIntosh.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 7-4! Robert Church cuts past defender and sends his shot off goalie and post and in. Second of game for Church.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 6-3! Jeremy Thompson speeds in, gets right in front and sends a tricky bounce shot past Poulin.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush power-play goal and it's 5-2. Jeff Shattler's second of the night as he takes the feed in the tight from Robert Church and puts it home.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush go up 4-2 as Marty Dinsdale fires long-range rocket around screen as shot clock winds down.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush power-play goal by Mark Matthews makes it 3-2. Matthews absolutely guns it from the high slot right by Poulin's shoulder.

name: Saskatchewan Rush
tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal from Jeff Shattler and it's 2-0. Shattler grabs lucky bounce off endboards and rifles it home.

tweet: HE SCORES! @RBC #SaskRush goal and it's 1-0 as Robert Church quick-sticks sweet little pass from Ryan Keenan across the goalmouth.
